About Hi, Im a software developer. I hope that new technologies are making life better. I have been learning English for many years but I have difficulty in remembering new words. This is main reason for my idea which is a mobile application. I want to develop it same as assistant in learning English. To beginning with this idea, its very easy to use the app, you can write a list of words and set them home screen or lock screen on your mobile phone. whenever you use your mobile, you can see it. Why do I choose mobile application to develop my idea? - Mobile phone is easy to bring anywhere - Mobile phone is popular to connect many people on the World - You can download applications from store and use it Something about my idea and how to use it? - After you open app, you only choose a background theme, write a list of words that you will learn today. Then you set background on home screen or lock screen. - This application allows you to use settings as font size, font color, padding. - You use background theme from gallery. - Banh assistant will support if you forget the meaning of the words. What will this app have features in next version? - See history of cards which were created in the past - Improving Banh assistant as AI bot, it will look for images with per word that you wrote. - Fix errors and filter users feedback to update helpful application - More and more other features in my mind.
